    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality example. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
