    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine is strong and responsive, the transmission shifts smoothly without hesitation, and all essential electronics and climate controls are fully functional. While there may be some very minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and the exterior retains a healthy shine. It represents a reliable, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
